+0334:     def combine_model_info(self, SVGModelInfo new_info):

 0862:                 control = float(elements.pop()) + float(elements.pop()) * 1j
 0863:                 end = float(elements.pop()) + float(elements.pop()) * 1j
 0864: 
 0865:                 if not absolute:
 0866:                     control += current_pos
 0867:                     end += current_pos
 0868: 
 0869:                 segments.append(path.QuadraticBezier(current_pos, control, end))
 0870:                 current_pos = end
 0871: 
 0872:             elif command == 'T':
 0873:                 # Smooth curve. Control point is the "reflection" of
 0874:                 # the second control point in the previous path.
 0875: 
 0876:                 if last_command not in 'QT':
 0877:                     # If there is no previous command or if the previous command
 0878:                     # was not an Q, q, T or t, assume the first control point is
 0879:                     # coincident with the current point.
 0880:                     control = current_pos
 0881:                 else:
 0882:                     # The control point is assumed to be the reflection of
 0883:                     # the control point on the previous command relative
 0884:                     # to the current point.
 0885:                     control = current_pos + current_pos - segments[-1].control2
 0886: 
 0887:                 end = float(elements.pop()) + float(elements.pop()) * 1j
 0888: 
 0889:                 if not absolute:
 0890:                     control += current_pos
 0891:                     end += current_pos
 0892: 
 0893:                 segments.append(path.QuadraticBezier(current_pos, control, end))
